  <title>veg</title>
  <abstract>This is a photo-interpreted vegetation layer that is more detailed and done to higher more consistent standard than the forestwide vegetation layer (vege). Forest land is typed to a 5 acre minimum for federal and state ownership, 20 acre for private. 

To provide better information on non-commercial and riparian stand conditions, for use in Watershed Analysis.

The photo interperting was done by Will Koenitzer, and people trained by Will Koenitzer, to maintain consistancy. Photo interpreted from 1:12000 aerial photos flown 1989 - 1995. </abstract>
